name: Air Canada 787-8 Dreamliner [C-GHPT] First Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
Here we have Air Canada's second Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner, C-GHPT making it's first ever landing at Calgary International Airport, arriving from Toronto. This is the first time a 787 has landed at Calgary on a revenue flight!
